==English==
===Noun===
'''phaneromania'''
# An uncontrollable [[impulse]] to [[pick]] at a spot or growth on one's body; the habit of picking at [[scabs]], biting one's [[nails]], or picking [[pimple]]s. 
# The constant [[preoccupation]] with some [[external]] part of the body, as [[pluck]]ing the beard, pulling the lobe of the ear, etc.